org.eclipse.golo.compiler.ir

Class AbstractGoloIrVisitor

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.eclipse.golo.compiler.ir.AbstractGoloIrVisitor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    GoloIrVisitor

    public abstract class AbstractGoloIrVisitor
extends java.lang.Object
implements GoloIrVisitor
    Abstract IR Visitor.

    This visitor walk the IR tree, but do nothing. It can be used to implement specific IR visitors by overriding only the specific methods, like for example the ones used in the compilation check and transformation step.
